{"word":"G5465 - χαλάω - chaláō - khal-ah'-o - Let down","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χαλάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">chaláō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">khal-ah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Let down</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - இறக்கு, போடு"},{"paragraph":"1. to loosen, slacken, relax"},{"paragraph":"2. to let down from a higher place to a lower"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the base of <a href=\"#/G5490 - χάσμα - chásma - khas'-mah/5490\">G5490</a>; to <i>lower</i> (as into a <i>void</i>): - let down, strike.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}